{
 "name": "RPlog_Jedi_Purge_-_Priti_s_Death",
 "title": "Jedi Purge: Priti's Death",
 "summary": "On an ordinary scorching day at the Tatooine Jedi School, the student Aubrey Saralyn seeks out her friend Priti and the two head out to Cort's training apparatus for a friendly practice duel. Unseen, the already-fallen Cort approaches across the desert, his dark influence beginning to seep into the sparring. As they fence atop the ramps and tightropes, Priti scores a light touch on Aubrey's shoulder -- and the small defeat tips Aubrey into a cold, hateful place, the Force bending to her rage. Pressing a defenseless, blade-lowered Priti against a wall, Aubrey runs her through in cold blood. Priti dies forgiving her with serene words about the beauty of the Force, leaving a horrified Aubrey weeping over the body before she rises, hollow and changed.",
